    "Uni3D is an end-to-end pre-trained scalable 3D object encoder which aligns the 3D point cloud features with the image-text aligned features.",
    "Because of our method without the alignment stage, we can get the 3D features which latently align with text by using Ulip2 and Uni3D.",
